### R code


```{default}
Delivery Days % =
VAR SummarizedSalesTable =
    CALCULATETABLE (
        SUMMARIZE (
            Sales,
            Sales[Order Number],
            Sales[Order Date],
            Sales[Delivery Date]
        ),
        Store[State] = "Online"
    )
VAR CurrentxDays =
    SELECTEDVALUE ( Days[Days] )
VAR DeliveryDays =
    AVERAGEX ( SummarizedSalesTable, Sales[Delivery Date] - Sales[Order Date] )
VAR DeliveryDaysPct =
    CALCULATE (
        DeliveryDays,
        FILTER ( ALL ( Sales ), DeliveryDays <= CurrentxDays )
    )
RETURN
    DeliveryDaysPct
```
